  "1724990": {
    "name": "汉字狂想",
    "steam_appid": 1724990,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/588d430b27b44e7a7f8832dfe9ac3f98.poster.avif?t=1770979843\" width=616 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/588d430b27b44e7a7f8832dfe9ac3f98.webm?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/588d430b27b44e7a7f8832dfe9ac3f98.mp4?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每张卡牌都是一个<strong>汉字</strong>，生命值等于笔画数。战斗规则简明爽快。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >博大精深的汉字体系可能<strong>划分</strong>为人、物品、植物、鬼神等大量系列……游戏也完全依此设计。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >海量卡牌的卡牌Roguelike！当前的测试版本已超过千张。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/6690c09ec53d5b119f7ed01087823d8d.poster.avif?t=1770979843\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/6690c09ec53d5b119f7ed01087823d8d.webm?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/6690c09ec53d5b119f7ed01087823d8d.mp4?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/132b3646b6e7635cb737a04260f44640.poster.avif?t=1770979843\" width=616 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/132b3646b6e7635cb737a04260f44640.webm?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/132b3646b6e7635cb737a04260f44640.mp4?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于每个汉字都可代表一种事物，卡牌技能依照汉字本身的<strong>含义</strong>设计，巧妙独特，趣味极强。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >事物之间的<strong>相互影响</strong>对于卡牌来说也一样。例如《斧》可以砍伐树木系列卡牌，《油》可以强化《火》。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以上共同形成了丰富、网状的<strong>流派</strong>。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/d86ccddb55ffd4c6dd559b9b7e37ec27.poster.avif?t=1770979843\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/d86ccddb55ffd4c6dd559b9b7e37ec27.webm?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/d86ccddb55ffd4c6dd559b9b7e37ec27.mp4?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/b9334f8261da8e7e9a488062fa157245.poster.avif?t=1770979843\" width=616 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/b9334f8261da8e7e9a488062fa157245.webm?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/b9334f8261da8e7e9a488062fa157245.mp4?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多个汉字可以<strong>合成</strong>更高等级的汉字。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以继承原有技能，也可以选择新的独特技能。<strong>核心</strong>汉字的能力可以加速发育、扭转战局。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合字配方来自：《通用规范汉字表》一、二级汉字（约7000字）。意味着只要符合真实语法都可以合成。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/22b2174abd8d4fc76f32f71af33fc89e.poster.avif?t=1770979843\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/22b2174abd8d4fc76f32f71af33fc89e.webm?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/22b2174abd8d4fc76f32f71af33fc89e.mp4?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/0e7bf632e5198a6d9898264c0d07e9ab.poster.avif?t=1770979843\" width=616 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/0e7bf632e5198a6d9898264c0d07e9ab.webm?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/0e7bf632e5198a6d9898264c0d07e9ab.mp4?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡牌相邻即可<strong>组成</strong>词语或成语，并得到极大增强。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >很容易形成有趣的组合！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组词配方来自：《现代汉语词典》（约80000词）。意味着卡牌之间的“羁绊”无穷无尽。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/7be6793e43da555b191500321ce53d3e.poster.avif?t=1770979843\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/7be6793e43da555b191500321ce53d3e.webm?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/7be6793e43da555b191500321ce53d3e.mp4?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/122fd6fee85f36103eceb7e3e058f311.poster.avif?t=1770979843\" width=616 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/122fd6fee85f36103eceb7e3e058f311.webm?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/122fd6fee85f36103eceb7e3e058f311.mp4?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一本<strong>随机页面</strong>的书中冒险、战斗，领略传统文化的风采。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打出依照真实甲骨文设计的<strong>甲骨牌</strong>来获得强大效果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搜集来自人文历史作品的多元宇宙的<strong>宝物</strong>，寻找更高境界的挑战！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/36422c435a198b51069d227dec09049e.poster.avif?t=1770979843\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/36422c435a198b51069d227dec09049e.webm?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/36422c435a198b51069d227dec09049e.mp4?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/f972e5619872c8b8e867bf0a24f33fd1.poster.avif?t=1770979843\" width=616 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/f972e5619872c8b8e867bf0a24f33fd1.webm?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/f972e5619872c8b8e867bf0a24f33fd1.mp4?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏将支持仓颉编辑器和<strong>创意工坊</strong>，任何玩家都可以轻松自定义自己的汉字世界：</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡牌和技能，字库，词库，关卡，传承宝物……</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一场永不止息的文化之旅。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/5603eb1783f006d1122a6e2893c71c9c.poster.avif?t=1770979843\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/5603eb1783f006d1122a6e2893c71c9c.webm?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/5603eb1783f006d1122a6e2893c71c9c.mp4?t=1770979843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724990/extras/adb48b8cd012ee28b4a781298918334a.avif?t=1770979843\" width=616 height=240 /></span></p>",
